data.title: Pejabat Tun Abdullah Ahmad Badawi kini ada laman web rasmi
data.meta_description:
Pejabat Tun Abdullah Ahmad Badawi (PTAB) mewujudkan laman web rasminya iaitu www.ptab.jpm.my bagi memudahkan orang ramai mendapatkan maklumat mengenai bekas Perdana Menteri, Tun Abdullah Ahmad Badawi.

	Menurut kenyataan Jabatan Perdana Menteri hari ini, laman web itu juga diwujudkan untuk kemudahan orang ramai yang ingin mendapatkan maklumat...

‘You’re full of s---, you must quit,’ Secret Service chief told over failure to stop Trump shooting

The director of the US Secret Service was told she was “full of s---” during an excruciating congressional hearing in which she was told she should resign.

Sky News

How the sending of one photo led an 11-year-old girl to become a victim of physical sex abuse

A mother has told Sky News how her 11-year-old daughter was groomed into sending sexually explicit photographs of herself to men online and how this spiralled into physical sexual abuse. The Internet Watch Foundation (IWF) says this is a growing problem and self-generated child abuse images - where a child is encouraged by someone online into sexualised behaviour - now makes up a large proportion of the imagery that they are removing from the internet. It is calling on the new government to make keeping children safe online a priority.
